\id INT - Chongthu Bible [tcz] India
\mt1 BIBLE THU
\ip Pathen thu a hin, Yahweh Pakai lunggel chule eiho dinmun, huhhingna lampi, michonse ho nungjui chule tahsan chate ho kipana ding ho jouse amu sohkei in ahi. A Dan hi athengsel in, Athupeh ho hi adetchet e, Athusim jong adih in, thumakai achepi ho jouse jong a hing jingin, a kikhel poi. Chih nadingin Pathen Pathen thu hi sim jingin, na pui houi dingin tahsan in, A thu theng hi kihil sah jingin. Achutileh, Yahweh Pakai thu chu nang dinga na lamjot na lampi salvah a pang ding, na gilkel ni jongleh nava sah ding , na chol ni le jong na kipasah ding ahi. Pathen Pathen thu hi kholjin lamjot pa a dinga a lam ko jangpeh a pang ahi, mun gamla jot pa dinga a teng gol chule thal choipa dinga a chem jam chule a tahsan pa dinga kihilna Dan buh ahi. Hiche ahin Van gam a ki hong in, Damun meidil kotpi jong akitah lang in ahi. Pathen Pathen thu a hin Yeshuwa Christa chu athu bul pen ahin, chule eiho phatna ding dungjuiya thu hung kisem ahi, hichejouse hi Pathen loupina dinga ahi. I lunggel sung uva ichen sah diu, athu bul hi ipom chah kheh dingu chuleh thu hin i keng se na lampi u jong a hil ding ikipui sah dingu ahi. Ani seh in taona to thon,(Rome 12:12) ki no lou vin sim jom jing u hite. Ajeh chu Pathen Pathen thu hi haona, loupina le kipana sangpen hungkon na ahi. Na damlai a Yahweh Pakai thu hi nakipe ahin, hinlah na ki kou tou ni tengleh, na hinlai thu ki tan bep ding ahi. Hijeh chun Pathen Pathen thu hi eleiset damlai uhin epoh gih u lenpen ahi, aga jong alou pi pen, a thupen ahi, totna le kichepna a nei ho jong a nikho a thu kitan ding ki haimil louding ahi. 
